Sounds good in theory, but the reality is that LDoN raids are pretty damn hard.  To gear up 36 people through LDoN adventures to a point that they'd stand a chance in one of the raids would take an extremely long time (unless you've got a bunch of just super hardcore LDoN'ers).  If SoE added some raids for people in NToV-quality gear, I think this idea becomes much more viable.  Anyhow, good luck with it.  I hope you're successful.<br>
